snd-hda-codec-cs8409-imac (1.14) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Speakers: restore amp->TDM channel map 0/2/1/3. The 4.0 surround test
    confirmed the physical wiring (0xd8=L tweeter, 0xda=L woofer, 0xdc=R
    tweeter, 0xde=R woofer); this map puts L on both left speakers and R on
    both right, driving all four with correct stereo. The 1.12/1.13 maps were
    chasing mono test files and summed L+R per side.

 -- Peter Shev <peter@shev.it>  Thu, 18 Jun 2026 20:40:00 +0000

